<div class="paragraph">
<p>In image 1, you can see that <strong>items coming from the webshop</strong> generated a <strong>revenue</strong> of <strong>349.61 Euros</strong>. Furthermore, you can see that this is <strong>46.25 percent</strong> of the total revenue that was generated by all referrers.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
